{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-3de0c339-0f0d-4983-a62c-b6406f6a84da-38\nfc_68d63ca7-99d1-9229-9dad-6cbf2d63fe01_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/13-工具与能力注册.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 13. 工具与能力注册（ToolRegistry）\n\n相关：[01-CallCard数据模型](./01-CallCard数据模型.md) · [15-动态出口与通话中工具事件](./15-动态出口与通话中工具事件.md) · [50-对话与模型适配](./50-对话与模型适配.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)\n\n## 1. 问题\n\n卡上仅有 `toolPolicy.allowedToolIds: string[]` 不够：编辑器不能只填自由字符串；校验器需知道工具是否存在、是否允许用于 story/free、是否在 `playback_only` 下禁用。\n\n## 2. ToolRegistry 条目\n\n```ts\ninterface ToolDefinition {\n  toolId: string\n  displayName: string\n  description: string\n  inputSchema: unknown          // JSON Schema / Zod 导出\n  allowedCardKinds: Array<\"free\" | \"story\" | \"system\">\n  /** 为 false 时任何 playback 阶段不可用 */\n  allowedInPlayback: boolean\n  runtimeGuards?: {\n    requiresStoryLock?: boolean\n    requiresCanIntroduce?: boolean\n    maxCallsPerSession?: number\n  }\n  /**\n   * 工具语义：\n   * - register_exit: 只登记 RuntimeExitCandidate（默认推荐）\n   * - session_local: 仅影响本通会话展示（极少）\n   */\n  behavior: \"register_exit\" | \"session_local\"\n  /** 登记出口时的模板（可选）；挂机才实例化为 Effect */\n  exitCandidateTemplate?: {\n    exitKind?: ExitKind\n    priority?: number\n    effectTemplateIds?: string[]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n- `register_exit`：通话中只登记 candidate，挂机后 Effect。  \n- `session_local`：**只读或仅本通展示**（如记忆召回）；**不写 Profile / Memory DB 业务态**（查询结果回给模型即可）。\n\n**v1 真源 = 引擎代码内置**（`builtinRegistry` / `@airpc/rpg-engine` 门面导出）；内容包可扩展须另立项接线，当前 **未知 toolId = 校验 error**。\n\n**与旧话机差异（定稿）：**  \ndoubaoSister 在通话中 FC handler **立刻写 store/调度/挂机**。本引擎一律改为：通话中只 `register_exit` → 挂机后 ExitSelector / FreeCallPostPipeline → Effect（+ Sink）。挂机类 FC **不进**引擎 Registry（见 §7.2）。  \n旧仓是**功能参考**，不是实现继承；inputSchema 见 §6.1。\n\n## 3. 与 toolPolicy\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":191,"fileSize":10436,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/13-工具与能力注册.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-3de0c339-0f0d-4983-a62c-b6406f6a84da-38\nfc_68d63ca7-99d1-9229-9dad-6cbf2d63fe01_4","startedAtMs":"1784768207952","completedAtMs":"1784768208100"},"model_call_id":"d1a062e0-df04-41ef-8d6a-b97759db341f-8-jcyu","session_id":"2f03fd97-78a6-4c45-8025-3dd48c837c63","timestamp_ms":1784768208071}
