{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-01fac180-a5bf-4875-a658-850c08b5bbcd-49\nfc_5592b548-14e7-99df-9121-65052f47ae1e_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/FloatingPanelShell.tsx","offset":100},"result":{"success":{"content":"\treturn (\n\t\t<aside\n\t\t\tref={panelRef}\n\t\t\tclassName={styles.panel}\n\t\t\tstyle={panelStyle}\n\t\t\taria-label={`${panelTitle}浮窗`}\n\t\t>\n\t\t\t<div className={styles.head}>\n\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了div拖拽区，用于按住标题栏移动浮窗 */}\n\t\t\t\t<div className={styles.dragZone} onMouseDown={onDragStart}>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span className={styles.grip} aria-hidden>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t⠿\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了Typography组件，用于浮窗标题 */}\n\t\t\t\t\t<Typography variant=\"subtitle2\" className={styles.title}>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t{panelTitle}\n\t\t\t\t\t</Typography>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了Button组件，用于关闭浮窗 */}\n\t\t\t\t<Button size=\"small\" onClick={onClose} aria-label=\"关闭浮窗\">\n\t\t\t\t\t关闭\n\t\t\t\t</Button>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t{/* 引用了Typography组件，用于不写盘提示 */}\n\t\t\t<Typography variant=\"caption\" className={styles.hint}>\n\t\t\t\t编辑本地投影；点顶栏「保存」整包写回 data/storis-packages。\n\t\t\t</Typography>\n\t\t\t{selection.selectionKind === \"chapter\" ? (\n\t\t\t\t// 引用了Formik组件，用于章节属性表单状态\n\t\t\t\t<Formik\n\t\t\t\t\tinitialValues={toChapterPropertyFormValues(selection.data)}\n\t\t\t\t\tenableReinitialize\n\t\t\t\t\tvalidate={validateChapterPropertyForm}\n\t\t\t\t\tonSubmit={(values, helpers) =>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsubmitChapterPropertyForm({\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdata: selection.data,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnodeId: selection.nodeId,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tvalues,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thelpers,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonApplyChapterNodeData,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tchapterDiskCtx,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\t{(formik) => (\n\t\t\t\t\t\t// 引用了ChapterPropertyForm组件，用于章节起止字段\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ChapterPropertyForm\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnodeData={selection.data}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tformik={formik}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tchapterDiskCtx={chapterDiskCtx}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tchapterPackageOptions={chapterPackageOptions}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t\t\t)}\n\t\t\t\t</Formik>\n\t\t\t) : (\n\t\t\t\t// 引用了Formik组件，用于 CallCard 属性表单状态\n\t\t\t\t<Formik\n\t\t\t\t\tinitialValues={toNodePropertyFormValues(selection.data)}\n\t\t\t\t\tenableReinitialize\n\t\t\t\t\tvalidate={validateNodePropertyForm}\n\t\t\t\t\tonSubmit={(values, helpers) =>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsubmitCallCardPropertyForm({\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdata: selection.data,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnodeId: selection.nodeId,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tvalues,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thelpers,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonApplyNodeData,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\t{(formik) => (\n\t\t\t\t\t\t// 引用了NodePropertyForm组件，用于 CallCard 属性字段\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<NodePropertyForm\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnodeData={selection.data}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tformik={formik}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcharacterAnchors={characterAnchors}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\teffectPanelSources={effectPanelSources}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonAssignOwner={(agentId, displayName) => {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tonAssignOwner(\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tselection.nodeId,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tagentId,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdisplayName,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t}}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t\t\t)}\n\t\t\t\t</Formik>\n\t\t\t)}\n\t\t</aside>\n\t);\n};\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":191,"fileSize":6467,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/FloatingPanelShell.tsx","readRange":{"startLine":100,"endLine":191},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-01fac180-a5bf-4875-a658-850c08b5bbcd-49\nfc_5592b548-14e7-99df-9121-65052f47ae1e_4","startedAtMs":"1784768221218","completedAtMs":"1784768221365"},"model_call_id":"d1a062e0-df04-41ef-8d6a-b97759db341f-10-yhmc","session_id":"2f03fd97-78a6-4c45-8025-3dd48c837c63","timestamp_ms":1784768221336}
